::Zardus::

Zardus sighs. "There's a battle nearby. Follow me but stay out of the way, 
and watch."

He walks out of the Alliance base, recieving Battera's transmission. He 
smiles. A message from Feline was probably good news, its been a while since 
he sent them on the mission.

"You may land," he replies, "But hurry, there's a battle I must get to."
